  <title translate="true">English Joke</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">English Joke</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Joke: A dwarf, clairvoyant escaped from jail. The police put out a statement that there is a &apos;Small Medium at Large&apos;. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Native English speakers will understand this Joke. &#160;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To explain to speakers of English as a second language.. </text></para>
          <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true">The term for a &apos;Dwarf Person&apos; is a &apos;Small Person&apos;. </text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true">The term for a &apos;Clairvoyant&apos; (a person who can foretell the future) is also &apos;a Medium&apos;.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true">The term for a person who has &apos;escaped from jail&apos; is someone who is &apos;at large&apos;, especially a Police term.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" translate="true">Small, Medium and Large are all Size Related, of course.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">So, when the Police say: &apos;A Small, Medium is at Large&apos;, it is funny because the words are all size related yet the phrase actually means something entirely different. It is a play on words. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">It also explains why translating from English is sometimes not easy.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
